graph TD
    A["/stark-generate-docs invoked"] --> B{"--skill or --all\nspecified?"}
    B -->|Yes| D["Phase 2: Generate Docs\ngenerate_skill_docs.py"]
    B -->|No| C["Phase 1: Detect Changes\ngenerate_skill_docs.py --check"]
    C --> E{"Any stale\ndocs found?"}
